name: Lisa S. M. Zadeh
summary:
I've been intrigued by human anatomy from a very young age. In my opinion, health is the greatest thing one can have, so together with my passion to learn more about the human physiology I decided to dedicate my career to the improvement of the human health, specialising in the field of Dentistry. 
My work ethic can be described as: assertive, responsible, critical and efficient. I thrive in multidisciplinary teams working on complex cases. In addition to my work as a general dentist, I specialise in Aesthetic and Emergency Dentistry.
